        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！看车儿上都是我臣子的首级，好痛心也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（锦芙蓉） 裂肝肠！痛诛夷盈朝丧亡，郊野血汤汤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大师，此乃臣子分内之事，不必悲伤，我们趱路要紧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！为我一人，连累万人性命，是我累及他们了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（锦芙蓉） 添悲怆，叹忠魂飘飏，"
        },
        {
          "character": "女差",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "趱路！"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大师，那边许多犯妇来了，且闪过一边。"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是，是，是，闪过一边。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（程济、建文帝同下。女差上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "女差",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "趱路！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众犯妇同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众犯妇",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苦吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同雁芙蓉） 苍苍呼冤震响，"
        },
        {
          "character": "女差徙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他乡，徙他乡，你们不曾看见那些夫人小姐？砍的砍，剐的剐，还要发教坊，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同哭） 啊呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "女差",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓？怎么你们都睡倒了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众犯妇",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们鞋弓袜小，走不动了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "女差",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鞋弓袜小走不动？嘿！谁教你们当初，把这个脚，裹得这样一兜兜的，要讨老"
        },
        {
          "character": "众犯妇",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们实是走不动了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "女差",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？你们不走，招老娘的打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众犯妇",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同雁芙蓉） 啊呀天吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "女差",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "趱路！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众犯妇",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苦吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（女差、众犯妇同下。建文帝、程济同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好恼吓，好恼！纵然杀戮忠臣，与这些妇女们何干？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小桃映芙蓉） 惨听著哀号莽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这也是人间浩劫，天降灾殃了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小桃映芙蓉） 纵然是天灾降，"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "𠲔！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小桃映芙蓉） 恨少个裸衣挝鼓骂渔阳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "男差",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大师，后面又有许多犯官来了，我们再躲过一边。"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是，是，是，再躲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（建文帝、程济同下。男差、众犯官同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "男差",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "男差",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因你们要做忠臣，故此圣上特来奉请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众犯官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们久不为官，又来拿解，岂不冤枉？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同普天芙蓉） 山林隐甘学佯狂，"
        },
        {
          "character": "男差",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们有话，到圣上面前去讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众犯官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀呸！讲什么？要砍就砍罢了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "犯官甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，列位老先生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众犯官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老先生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "犯官甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "总是我们不是，当初无能御敌，直至纵虎归山，悔之晚矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众犯官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "男差",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一班不知死活的囚徒！"
        },
        {
          "character": "男差",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（男差、众犯官同下。建文帝、程济同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了吓罢了。我只道独诛戮朝中臣宰，不想又捕捉那些弃职官员。正人君子吓，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱奴插芙蓉） 眼见得普天受枉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大师，天色已晚，趱路要紧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！我想做忠臣的到这个地位，那些读书的，还要做什么官？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱奴插芙蓉） 我言非戆劝冠裳罢想，"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此处湖广要道，京中来往公干甚多，倘有识认，祸生不测。"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿呀！这便怎么处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不妨。我们且赶到武冈州，速往贵州，直至云南，深山居住，方可安身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此快走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大师请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（钟声。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咦？程徒，景阳钟鸣了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，大师，此乃野寺晚钟，非景阳钟也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗄！咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 错听了野寺钟鸣误景阳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大师趱路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（建文帝、程济同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
      ],
